text.section:
This section does not apply to:
State and federal wetlands;
Private wetlands as designated by the Department;
Land which qualifies for agricultural assessments, as provided under § 8-209 of the Tax - Property Article, and timberland and lands used for reforestation;
Except in Howard and Harford counties, owners and lessees of any privately owned land; and
Owners and lessees of any privately owned land in Howard and Harford counties as long as a trap described in subsection (a) of this section is not within 150 yards of the permanent residence of another person.
